	menu_cs_basement = "Підвал",
	menu_cs_basement_desc = "In the basement John Wick is setting up a shooting range, with Wolf's workshop right next door. At the other end, Sokol and Dragan have their gym and training facilities. Bodhi has set up a workshop for his surfboards, too. And then there's Jacket's corner.$NL;$NL;The basement is also home to the vault, where the gang keeps all that sweet loot.",
