	menu_cs_daily_challenge = "Побічні завдання",
	menu_cs_daily_desc = "Every day a heister in the safe house will have a challenge for you! Meet with them in the safe house to accept their challenge, and then go out into the world to complete the requirements. Complete the challenge, and they'll give you a few Continental Coins for your troubles.$NL;$NL;Wick managed to get the Payday crew membership to The Continental, so they're giving you coins for every heist you pull off. With enough coins, Charlie and his boys will come in and do a little redecorating for us, and make sure that any work done stays off the books.",
